        Return a string representation of ``self``.

        The type consists of :meth:`BinaryMatroid.bicycle_dimension` and
        :meth:`BinaryMatroid.brown_invariant`.

        EXAMPLES::

            sage: M = matroids.named_matroids.Fano()
            sage: M.rename()
            sage: repr(M)  # indirect doctest
